{"tid":1506979,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[我有交稅架]回帶：警員欠交稅金額飆四成 近8年新高","createTime":"2019-08-26T03:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T06:01:29.000Z","uid":33775,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e593d6efdab9d20ec53b6a3098d86062ae145a04","tid":1506979,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/police-12_sLa4r_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpolice-12_sLa4r_1200x0.png&h=36983288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n保安局本月向立法會提交文件披露，無力償債警務人員的最新統計數字。數字顯示，今年上半年無力償債警員的總數有所下跌，但欠交稅款的宗數、涉及總額有所上升，今年上半年稅局向警員發出48份追稅通知書，有關警員欠交的稅款合共達77萬元，按年飆四成，為近八年新高。<br />\n<br />\n今年上半年，稅局向警員發出的追討稅款通知書總數有48宗，是2011年上半年以來的新高。至於在同期，警員欠交的稅款達77萬港元，是近八年以來的新高。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，另有46名警員被列為「無力償債」，按年跌了一成，其中逾七成、即33名警員欠債原因涉及「家人和親友的問題」，3名警員涉及賭博欠債。<br />\n<br />\n年度（上半年） 已向警員出發的追稅通知書 欠稅涉款（港元）<br />\n2015 48 $770,056<br />\n2014 36 $538,323<br />\n2013 28 $552,868<br />\n2012 33 $300,070<br />\n2011 58 $636,158<br />\n2010 46 $430,424<br />\n2009 59 $414,822<br />\n2008 51 $575,309<br />\n資料來源：保安局<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%AC%A0%E4%BA%A4%E7%A8%85%E9%87%91%E9%A1%8D%E9%A3%86%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90-%E8%BF%918%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98/?fbclid=IwAR3laOHsK-LrS-CM7RrIkk2gRZgQ5Onp1_ypQ8qxVGz8WV1cTiAWoJnBQow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%25A8%2585%25E9%2587%2591%25E9%25A1%258D%25E9%25A3%2586%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2588%2590-%25E8%25BF%25918%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3laOHsK-LrS-CM7RrIkk2gRZgQ5Onp1_ypQ8qxVGz8WV1cTiAWoJnBQow&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxiSthV5vJK0WXiSTZm%2FaoTA%3D&h=d4b0efc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%